item.title: About
item.description: In a previous life, I worked on cross-functional projects in energy as an applied ML scientist w/ PETRONAS Research. Currently I build domain-specific generative AI applications as a technical co-founder at V-Cred. I code in my spare time, either for amusement (tnwei/vqgan-clip-app, These Nebulae Do Not Exist), out of curiosity (tnwei/waternet, tnwei/intrinsic-dimension), or to scratch personal itches (tnwei/python-rle, tnwei/msia-covid-api, tnwei/mlflow-docker). I hike semi-regularly on weekends. There’s a lot of good places to go in the KL / Klang valley area.
